model

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Entity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Enemy, Projectile, Tower

    public abstract class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    A general abstract Entity class used to represent different objects used and displayed in the game. Contains the information necessary to figure out the entities position on the board and how to draw it when it is retrieved.
    Author:
    Ethan Glasberg (glasberg@email.arizona.edu), Jarod Bristol (jarodkylebristol@email.arizona.edu), Alex Gonzalez (aegonzalez793@email.arizona.edu), Patrick Dearborn (pdearborn@email.arizona.edu)
